Text: If you want to convert the files using dbpoweramp, CLEAR the ID Tag first. I ran into and error while trying before doing this. If anyone knows anything about dbpoweramp, under properties, there is a section called ID-Tag. Under all the tags, there is a section called clear. You can do this to multiple files too.
